      },
      "width": 620,
      "height": 330,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# Lifecycle Smoke Procedure\n\n1. Open this graph and check **Lifecycle Hook Log** for `onLoad`.\n2. Add a new `lifecycle-probe` node from Legend to trigger `onCreate`.\n3. Edit `complaint` text on any `lifecycle-probe` node to trigger update hooks.\n4. Delete a `lifecycle-probe` node to trigger `onDelete`.\n\nExpected: each action appends a line to the log node."
      }
